{"tid":1573662,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"食完催淚彈 啲傷口唔識好","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T02:01:55.000Z","uid":34921,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e0507a1115cc8d03ef04bd58058858800a92ed","tid":1573662,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"以前都唔會咁<br />\n但而家損手爛腳咁<br />\n啲傷口會埋左層表皮 而且腫起小小<br />\n但入面唔識好<br />\n層表皮好易再爛過<br />\n係咁loop<br />\n新既傷口就無事<br />\n唔識好既全部都係食過煙<br />\n問過杏林<br />\n淨係叫我保持清潔<br />\n都唔知點搞好<br />\n<br />\nPs有另外既手足同我情況一樣"},{"pid":"f0daa8351d27a94d98a8843ec87b2376114c543e","tid":1573662,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiNgEaJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiNgEaJ.jpg&h=997fd935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=f74009a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=2fcbf4cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"63deeb30f716cb9c4eaaaa5f51da7fbda1d9de01","tid":1573662,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces