aces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"愛你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaf0831a8cfe30b99e03c877d9dfd437e1957c4","tid":1573662,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"如果只係普通外傷，可以試下３Ｍ嗰隻人工皮膠布<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nexcare.com.hk/3M/zh_HK/nexcare-hk/products/hydrocolloid/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexcare.com.hk%2F3M%2Fzh_HK%2Fnexcare-hk%2Fproducts%2Fhydrocolloid%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=9ff18e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nexcare.com.hk/3M/zh_HK/nexcare-hk/products/hydrocolloid/</a><br />\n佢係可以幫助到傷口快啲埋口，但都幾貴下，睇下負唔負擔到"},{"pid":"da24ce2224bb300ff3dd26e15c8b26d992c402ce","tid":1573662,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1eb35348a79328ddcdf7c783c317672637f8dde5","tid":1573662,"uid":124030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"用3m防水膠布/人做皮<br />\n你有咩敷料呀？<br />\n<br />\n我上月跌倒冇左忽肉<br />\n發炎好唔返<br />\n用下面呢隻敷料<br />\n好快好返<br />\n佢勁吸血同埋唔會痴住傷口<br />\n我去診所洗傷口，醫生都問係咩敷料<br />\n想幫診所入貨<br />\n你可能要去藥房/醫療鋪搵搵<br />\n<br />\n祝平安🙏🏻唔好濕水！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.molnlycke.ae/products-solutions/mepilex/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.molnlycke.ae%2Fproducts-solutions%2Fmepilex%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=4e7672b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.molnlycke.ae/products-solutions/mepilex/</a>"},{"pid":"e889cb12f915f79fc0dc29c799b1e0d59a11c0dc","tid":1573662,"uid":124030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"記得用生理鹽水洗傷口！"},{"pid":"6984f2d9681a02422937c9a47bfccbd01b1501b7","tid":1573662,"uid":124030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"如有膿/發炎就用粉紅色消毒鹽水沖"},{"pid":"2d75088831f0b6d3196b7b6a1123adcf2a4f43a2","tid":1573662,"uid":173060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"同上面巴打講既一樣，生理鹽水洗傷口，洗傷口有手勢，棉球浸濕向一個方向抹，忍到痛既大力少少抹乾淨，膠布早晚換，有膿流出既勤d換，傷口保持乾爽唔好濕水"},{"pid":"fb36291ad9f5ef2babf2ea15eccc7012d189a55e","tid":1573662,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48141fb0c8dce858016cd4a929731d26add30a36","tid":1573662,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63deeb30f716cb9c4eaaaa5f51da7fbda1d9de01","tid":1573662,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"愛你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"咁用花士令"},{"pid":"c18403effc0a0d6343adbfbbb8e89058241ee29b","tid":1573662,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8e0507a1115cc8d03ef04bd58058858800a92ed","tid":1573662,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"以前都唔會咁<br />\n但而家損手爛腳咁<br />\n啲傷口會埋左層表皮 而且腫起小小<br />\n但入面唔識好<br />\n層表皮好易再爛過<br />\n係咁loop<br />\n新既傷口就無事<br />\n唔識好既全部都係食過煙<br />\n問過杏林<br />\n淨係叫我保持清潔<br />\n都唔知點搞好<br />\n<br />\nPs有另外既手足同我情況一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"免疫系統問題，你唔夠休息、唔夠營養，傷口有冇消毒？有冇食抗生素？"},{"pid":"f0a26f4c105c43fb90e9180369fb1e806d436899","tid":1573662,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"隻手開始會甩皮"},{"pid":"440e108038c251d60b579eb06a95e0f94227551c","tid":1573662,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c18403effc0a0d6343adbfbbb8e89058241ee29b","tid":1